<%- title "your membership" -%>

<p>Hello, <%= current_user.email %>. You are <%= @membership.full_name %> of Ruby Together.</p>

<p>
  Your membership is currently <%= @membership.status %>
  <%- if @membership.active? -%>
    , and monthly membership dues will be charged to your <%= @membership.card_brand %> ending in <%= @membership.card_last4 %>
  <%- end -%>
  .
</p>

<p>
  <%- if @membership.name -%>
    You are credited on our members page as "<%= @membership.name %>".</p>
  <%- else -%>
    You are not credited on our <%= link_to "members page", members_path %>. If you'd like to be credited, we can add your name.
  <%- end -%>
<p>

<p>If you need help with your membership, please <%= contact_us %>.</p>
